(25, 1, 3, 2, 13, 1, '<img width="107" height="164" src="media/News-Images/Small/NPC-small.png" style="margin: -10px 10px 10px; float: right;" alt="" />Here is a new release featuring the NPC actors. Now the worlds of<br />\r\nLbanet will be much more lively that they were before! A few new<br />\r\nfeatures are also coming with the NPC.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href="news.php">... More details</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />', 1, 0, 1, 1260059591, 1260483303),
