(29, 2, 3, 2, 13, 1, 'Here is a new release featuring the NPC actors. Now the worlds of<br />\r\nLbanet will be much more lively that they were before! A few new<br />\r\nfeatures are also coming with the NPC.\r\n<p>Here is a complete list of the ne<img width="445" vspace="10px" hspace="10px" height="449" align="right" src="media/News-Images/Big/NPC.png" alt="" />w features:</p>\r\n<p>- Added NPC actors. They are fully animated however they is no real<br />\r\ndialog yet. You can already talk to them but they will not say<br />\r\nanything.</p>\r\n<p>- Added merchants. You can now buy items from some of the NPC all over the maps.</p>\r\n<p>- Added actor travel feature. You should now be able to take use the<br />\r\nferries but also the cars and motorbikes.</p>\r\n<p>- Added scripted zone. Just try to hide in the trash in the map out of<br />\r\ncitadel prison ;)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 1, 0, 1, 1260060784, 1260062061),
