(51, 1, 3, 1, 13, 1, 'The LBANet-Team wishes you a merry merry Christmas and has got a little surprise for you.<br />\r\n&quot;The LBANet-Christmas-Party-Event&quot;!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHere''s how to join the Party!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou should now all be ported to the Christmas-Event when you connect.<br />\r\nIf you accidently ported out or you have just registered you can (re-)enter the Christmas-Event either through sendel''s well or by selecting &quot;Party place&quot; in your teleport-box.<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color: rgb(167, 250, 250);"><a href="cms://idcatside=2">... More details</a> </span> <br />', 1, 0, 1, 1261672115, 1261672115),
