(55, 2, 3, 1, 13, 1, 'The LBANet-Team wishes you a merry merry Christmas and has got a little surprise for you.<br />\r\n&quot;The LBANet-Christmas-Party-Event&quot;!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHere''s how to join the Party!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou should now all be ported to the Christmas-Event when you connect.<br />\r\nIf you accidently ported out or you have just registered you can (re-)enter the Christmas-Event either through sendel''s well or by selecting &quot;Party place&quot; in your teleport-box.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Christmas update features:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-The Citadel-Island-Party-Scene has been modified for the ultimate Christmas-event!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-There are all new Items including e.g. Christmas-Canes, Champagne and Lebkuchen<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-All the NPCs at the Event-place have got different dialogs that make sense(!)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Santa Clause ! (and other special Christmas-NPCs)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSo, we wish you a merry merry christmas and hope you have fun with our little Christmas Gift.', 1, 0, 1, 1261672381, 1261672381),
