(1, 1, 1, 1, 0, '2009-12-06 00:00:00', 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'New Release v0.75', '', 'Here is a new release featuring the NPC actors. <img style="float: right; margin: 10px;" src="index.php/index.php/index.php/index.php/index.php/media/News-Images/Big/NPC.png" alt="" /><br />Now the worlds of Lbanet will be much more lively that they were before!<br />A few new features are also coming with the NPC.\r\n<p>Here is a complete list of the ne<img src="index.php/index.php/index.php/media/News-Images/Big/NPC.png" alt="" align="right" />w features:</p>\r\n<p>- Added NPC actors. They are fully animated however they is no real<br /> dialog yet. You can already talk to them but they will not say<br /> anything.</p>\r\n<p>- Added merchants. You can now buy items from some of the NPC all over the maps.</p>\r\n<p>- Added actor travel feature. You should now be able to take use the<br /> ferries but also the cars and motorbikes.</p>\r\n<p>- Added scripted zone. Just try to hide in the trash in the map out of<br /> citadel prison ;)</p>\r\n<img style="float: right; margin: 10px 10px 10px 0;" src="index.php/index.php/index.php/index.php/index.php/index.php/index.php/index.php/index.php/index.php/index.php/index.php/media/News-Images/Small/NPC-small.png" alt="" />', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, '2009-12-10 23:30:45', '2009-12-24 17:30:35', '1fde57876edcbf77480ac64995ab5c75'),
(2, 1, 2, 0, 0, '2009-12-06 00:00:00', 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'New Release v0.75', '', 'Here is a new release featuring the NPC actors. Now the worlds of<br /> Lbanet will be much more lively that they were before! A few new<br /> features are also coming with the NPC. <img style="float: right; margin: 10px 10px 10px 0;" src="index.php/index.php/media/News-Images/Small/NPC-small.png" alt="" />', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, '2009-12-10 23:30:45', '2009-12-10 23:30:45', '1fde57876edcbf77480ac64995ab5c75'),
(3, 1, 1, 1, 0, '2009-12-24 00:00:00', 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'LBANet v0.755 - Christmas Event:', '', 'The LBANet-Team wishes you a merry merry Christmas and has got a little surprise for you.<br /> "The LBANet-Christmas-Party-Event"!<br /> <br /> Here''s how to join the Party!<br /> <br /> You should now all be ported to the Christmas-Event when you connect.<br /> If you accidently ported out or you have just registered you can (re-)enter the Christmas-Event either through sendel''s well or by selecting "Party place" in your teleport-box.<br /><br /><br /> The Christmas update features:<br /> <br /> -The Citadel-Island-Party-Scene has been modified for the ultimate Christmas-event!<br /> <br /> -There are all new Items including e.g. Christmas-Canes, Champagne and Lebkuchen<br /> <br /> -All the NPCs at the Event-place have got different dialogs that make sense(!)<br /> <br /> -Santa Clause ! (and other special Christmas-NPCs)<br /> <br /> So, we wish you a merry merry christmas and hope you have fun with our little Christmas Gift.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, '2009-12-24 17:31:24', '2009-12-24 17:32:12', 'bcd4138beb347bbe5d8ca7c8ee28f0f3'),
(4, 1, 2, 0, 0, '2009-12-24 00:00:00', 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'LBANet v0.755 - Christmas Event:', '', 'The LBANet-Team wishes you a merry merry Christmas and has got a little surprise for you.<br /> "The LBANet-Christmas-Party-Event"!<br /> <br /> Here''s how to join the Party!<br /> <br /> You should now all be ported to the Christmas-Event when you connect.<br /> If you accidently ported out or you have just registered you can (re-)enter the Christmas-Event either through sendel''s well or by selecting "Party place" in your teleport-box.<br /><br /><br /> The Christmas update features:<br /> <br /> -The Citadel-Island-Party-Scene has been modified for the ultimate Christmas-event!<br /> <br /> -There are all new Items including e.g. Christmas-Canes, Champagne and Lebkuchen<br /> <br /> -All the NPCs at the Event-place have got different dialogs that make sense(!)<br /> <br /> -Santa Clause ! (and other special Christmas-NPCs)<br /> <br /> So, we wish you a merry merry christmas and hope you have fun with our little Christmas Gift.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, '2009-12-24 17:31:24', '2009-12-24 17:31:24', 'bcd4138beb347bbe5d8ca7c8ee28f0f3');
